{"TopicId":159317,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"What Would A Kerbal Movie Be About?","CreatedByName":"KAL 9000","CreatedById":140704,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T01:02:36Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"KAL 9000","CreatedById":140704,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T01:02:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think we all agree that KSP would look great on the big screen. WE COULD GET MOAR BACKSTORY YAY!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyway, let\u0027s say it\u0027s five years in the future. KSP has become as popular as Minecraft (hopefully), and some film studios are thinking about making a movie.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe bring a good director, excellent staff,\u00A0and talented actors on board, as well as a $500 million budget (totally not realistic, but this is hypothetical).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWHAT DO YOU WANT THE KERBAL MOVIE TO BE ABOUT?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSome of my ideas:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-The beginnings of the space program\u00A0(Think the Right Stuff and Apollo 13 with Kerbals)\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-The Dunian (It sells itself!)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Kerbfleet: The Movie\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-Spy thriller starring Special Agent Kirrim\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat ideas do you have?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"cubinator","CreatedById":150330,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T02:21:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA mission to Jool that loses contact with home halfway there, and finds some strange stuff... *cough* \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69224-cydonian-monk/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002269224\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/69224-cydonian-monk/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Cydonian Monk\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0*cough*\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WinkAllKerb\u0026#039;\u0026#039;","CreatedById":78047,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T02:24:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwell i think about this\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022taco-tuesday.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://www.larp.com/jay/pics/taco-tuesday.jpg\u0022\u003E, ksp lego is what you need \u00A0or tralala megablock tralalal [insert copyright \u002B whatever block \u002B format c: /defrag ...], and you know me and copyright are not exactly what we can call great friend]\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-17T02:26:40Z\u0022 title=\u002204/17/2017 02:26  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 17, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by WinkAllKerb\u0026#039;\u0026#039;\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex","CreatedById":75164,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T03:26:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s my personal belief that video game movies, particularly ones about open-world or sandbox-style games are destined to fail because they were originally designed with player choice in mind. I think that for these types of games, if you want to relinquish control over the game, just look at some let\u0027s plays and other entertainment for the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHOWEVER, for the sake of the hypothetical situation, I wouldn\u0027t be opposed to seeing some kind of brief origin story of how the Kerbals came to be and settle at their current \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E. Maybe with some early spaceflight triumphs thrown in- or perhaps the climax is when Jeb finally gets to space for the very first time and is awestruck by the sight of Kerbin in his window. Now that would look amazing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WinkAllKerb\u0026#039;\u0026#039;","CreatedByI