s/ZNGIcon1.png\u0022 title=\u0022:/\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WinkAllKerb\u0026#039;\u0026#039;","CreatedById":78047,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T04:02:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyep max you know it\u0027s sort of will smith opening the case in scene in the train station in mib, same concept/maetpahor different backround and caracter\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZooNamedGames","CreatedById":103726,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T04:11:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027d be about me.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn all seriousness, I have a story.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"WinkAllKerb\u0026#039;\u0026#039;","CreatedById":78047,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T04:41:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\na yup this story ... you \u0026amp; me \u0026amp; you\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T06:18:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis will be a saga about a little boy who had a dream.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSpace, rockets, other planets, light of the cold bright stars far away...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNobody was understanding him, everybody was mocking him, but he held on and didn\u0027t surrender.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHe was unlike the others.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd his dream has gotten fulfilled. He had never built a rocket and never flied into space, as others. He has kept his individuality.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhile others\u00A0were madding around the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E launching stuff because there was absolutely nothing to do on their Kerbin except exploration,\u00A0he wanted just to sit at home and play tetris.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-17T06:19:11Z\u0022 title=\u002204/17/2017 06:19  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 17, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RA3236","CreatedById":150734,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T08:59:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223023731\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492400887\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278047\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022WinkAllKerb\u0027\u0027\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, WinkAllKerb\u0027\u0027 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nit prolly has to do with \u0022ra\u0022, i mean you know that thing floating in the sky that make grow stuff sending photon and slowly dying each time it send photon to make stuff grow, in the meanwhile this thing float in something even bigger with something really weird in the center ... call the grox ....\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHuh? I heard my name. Oh? What? Your talking about the guy with the lowercase name? Ok then.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T09:20:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223023903\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492419563\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150734\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022RA3236\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 minutes ago, RA3236 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHuh? I heard my name. Oh? What? Your talking about the guy with the lowercase name? Ok then.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProtocol 21 activated. Yellow code. Please stay still until the process complete. 3... 2... 1... Okay, Response positive. Thank you for your co-operation.\u003Cbr\u003E\nTest subject model RA\u00A0ser.no. 3236 is successfully terminated. Activating RA #3237.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"adsii1970","CreatedById":89014,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T11:21:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy not take it in a different direction... and put the focus where it is due... on \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/4-harvester/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u00224\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/4-harvester/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HarvesteR\u003C/a\u003E and his vision for an awesome game... then chronicle the development of KSP from the early roots, etc. to Squad now... And to break the scenes in the movie, have a snippet from the game - maybe a minute and a half, all the way from the beginning, to ending the movie with credits going over some more recent Scott Manley videos... Make it one freaking long commercial about KSP...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RA3236","CreatedById":150734,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T11:30:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223023922\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492420838\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022129408\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022kerbiloid\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, kerbiloid said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nProtocol 21 activated. Yellow code. Please stay still until the process complete. 3... 2... 1... Okay, Response positive. Thank you for your co-operation.\u003Cbr\u003E\nTest subject model RA\u00A0ser.no. 3236 is successfully terminated. Activating RA #3237.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003E[ERROR] Termination unsuccessful:\nMODEL RA3236, FUNCTION: GAMER\nERROR REPORT UNSUCCESSFUL\nEMERGENCY OVERRIDE ACTIVATE\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MiffedStarfish","CreatedById":175356,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T11:43:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI personally think actors wouldn\u0027t work. I think a cross between the styles of hatbat and nassualt and the\u00A0cinematics made for uptdates\u00A0would look great on a big screen, but I\u0027m not sure a film would be a great thing.\u00A0The story\u00A0of the kerbals and\u00A0game is underdeveloped because the focus is on orbital mechanics and simulating\u00A0realistic space flight, which would be hard to represent in a film.\u00A0kerbals verbally don\u0027t speak, except for some tutorial like writing dialogue, and the game in general was never meant to have lore, (which I\u0027m not saying is a good thing) and I think the franchise would work a lot better in books and such, as stories written in fan works prove.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTL;DR I don\u0027t think the franchise would work in a hour\u002B\u00A0film, I think it would be better with overwatch-style animated shorts documenting momentous occasions and possibly comics.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T12:00:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA spin-off. \u003Cem\u003EKerbals: The Community\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeveral thousand people sitting before computers and smartphones looking at the forum page, typing something and from time to time laughing or screaming.\u003Cbr\u003E\n(Hot news: 2nd season is confirmed.)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-17T12:00:28Z\u0022 title=\u002204/17/2017 12:00  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 17, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by kerbiloid\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DarkOwl57","CreatedById":161624,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T12:49:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223023754\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492402316\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022103726\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ZooNamedGames\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, ZooNamedGames said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027d be about me.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn all seriousness, I have a story.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyeah. You and about 600 more writers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn all seriousness, the movie would be like \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u