SK\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s writing to film?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Just Jim","CreatedById":148725,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T13:06:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223024098\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492433387\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161624\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DarkOwl57\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, DarkOwl57 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyeah. You and about 600 more writers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn all seriousness, the movie would be like \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022148725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Just Jim\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s \u0022Emiko Station\u0022 Or \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/111501-kuzzter/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022111501\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/111501-kuzzter/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Kuzzter\u003C/a\u003E\u0027s \u0022Kerbfleet\u0022\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis might sound a little weird, but if \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002266485\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/66485-squad/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SQUAD\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0did reach out for me to write a screenplay... and ideally it would be a joint effort with my buddy\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/111501-kuzzter/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022111501\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/111501-kuzzter/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Kuzzter\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0and other writers, and not just by myself... I don\u0027t know if I\u0027d want to do\u00A0Emiko. Don\u0027t misunderstand, I love writing Emiko Station, and I\u0027m having all sorts of fun, but I\u0027ll be the first to admit, it\u0027s a little \u0022out-there\u0022, and probably not for everyone.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZooNamedGames","CreatedById":103726,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T13:35:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWish my style could be appreciated next to \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022148725\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/148725-just-jim/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Just Jim\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0and \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/61025-ksk/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002261025\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/61025-ksk/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@KSK\u003C/a\u003E. But alas, I\u0027m no one despite trying my best to give this community an original story. I\u0027ve even tried like 3 times to see it made into a cinematic.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGrumble grumble. Just started a new series too. What more can I do.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DarkOwl57","CreatedById":161624,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T13:44:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223023596\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492390956\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022140704\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KAL 9000\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, KAL 9000 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think we all agree that KSP would look great on the big screen. WE COULD GET MOAR BACKSTORY YAY!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsi\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223023596\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492390956\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022140704\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KAL 9000\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, KAL 9000 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyway, let\u0027s say it\u0027s five years in the future. KSP has become as popular as Minecraft (hopefully), and some film studios are thinking about making a movie.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMinecraft has a movie?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223023596\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492390956\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022140704\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KAL 9000\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, KAL 9000 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWe bring a good director, excellent staff,\u00A0and talented actors on board\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n*whispers* Please be the Hunger Games cast. Please be the Hunger Games cast...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223023596\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492390956\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022140704\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KAL 9000\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, KAL 9000 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nas well as a $500 million budget (totally not realistic, but this is hypothetical).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHOLY! I don\u0027t think a movie has\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eever\u003C/em\u003E had that big of a budget...........\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"TheKosanianMethod","CreatedById":163034,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T13:53:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223024157\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492436699\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161624\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DarkOwl57\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 minutes ago, DarkOwl57 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHOLY! I don\u0027t think a movie has\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eever\u003C/em\u003E had that big of a budget...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe only movie close to that would be Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides. It took the Hobbit\u00A0Trilogy to get to $623 million - or about $200 million a movie.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DarkOwl57","CreatedById":161624,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T14:03:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223024164\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022159317\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221492437218\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022163034\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022TheKosanianMethod\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 minutes ago, TheKosanianMethod said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe only movie close to that would be Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides. It took the Hobbit\u00A0Trilogy to get to $623 million - or about $200 million a movie.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDang! I\u0027d like to see how big a budget a series like the Fast and Furious took (With..... 8? 9 movies?) Gotta be at least 500. But 500 for one movie?!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Brent Kerman","CreatedById":167451,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-17T14:05:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI would say this would be my preference:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Kerbfleet\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. First Flight\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. Plan Kappa\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4. Emiko Station\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5. The Asteroid Sentinels\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut, we have Nasult, we have \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89536-hatbat/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002289536\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/89536-hatbat/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@HatBat\u003C/a\u003E, there are others as well. I think a cooperation of the best minds could make something epic. And I would put any help I could if needed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-17T14:08:29Z\u0022 title=\u002204/17/2017 02:08  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 17, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Brent Kerman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"}]}